   this document replaces Section 5.2 of [RFC2247].

It should say:

   The description of the 'domain' object class provided in this
|  document supersedes that found in RFC 2247.  That is, Section 3.4 of
   this document replaces Section 5.2 of [RFC2247].


(3)  extraneous (duplicated) text

