         for m = all routes still under consideration
|            for n = all routes in still under consideration
                 if (cost(n) is lower than cost(m))
                     remove m from consideration

where it should say:

         for m = all routes still under consideration
|            for n = all other routes in still under consideration
                 if (cost(n) is lower than cost(m))
                     remove m from consideration


