Section 4.2 says:
 
   <dialog-info xmlns="urn:ietf:params:xml:ns:dialog-info"
    xmlns:xsi=" <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance>
http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"
